						               													<description>The Madoushi miniature is a substitute option for any Ninja at the start of the PvP Dawn Escape game. It was originally offered as a reward for certain backers of the Dized Kickstarter campaign in December 2018.&amp;#10; Madoushi has disguised himself as a Ninja in the Midnight Raid and now shows his true self to use his magi and steal the glory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;House Rules &amp;ndash;&amp;nbsp;who gets to play him (First or last Ninja on the Roof in the Midnight Raid etc.):&amp;#10;Simply replace your Ninja Miniature with the Madoushi miniature and swap your 3 Wana Tokens with the 3 Magic Cards.&amp;#10;Like the Wana Tokens, the Magic cards are single use and each should be discarded once used.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Magic Cards:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Yadoku (Poison Dart): Causes target to double up in pain and fall back to their last location.&amp;#10;     Makaze (Evil Wind): Opponent is lifted high into the air and moved by the Madoushi two tiles in any direction.&amp;#10;     Ky&amp;#197;&amp;#171;ketsu (Blood Leech): A vile flying leech conjured by the Madoushi will always find its target, even if in cover or not in line of sight. Effect: Knock-back (1 tile)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
